#!/bin/sh
d=$(date '+%a %b %d, %H:') j=$(date +%-M) p="0"
if [ "$j" -gt 9 ];then p="";fi
printf %s\\n "%{c}$d$p$j";sleep $((61-$(date +%-S)))
while true;do
p="0";while [ "$j" -lt 9 ];do
j=$((j+1));printf %s\\n "%{c}$d$p$j";sleep 60;done
p="";while [ "$j" -lt 59 ];do
j=$((j+1));printf %s\\n "%{c}$d$p$j";sleep 60;done
j=$(($(date +%-M)-1)) d=$(date '+%a %b %d, %H:');done
